 "remarks": "Definitely the one you&apos;ve been waiting for. It&apos;s in superb condition, it&apos;s in a coveted location and it&apos;s on a level &quot;playing field&quot; acre! The main floor, has a versatile open concept, is designed for today&apos;s lifestyle and allows your eye to travel uninterrupted from room to room to room. Windowed walls and an East/West exposure offer glorious sunrises and sunsets, flood the home with natural light all day long and bring the outdoors in. Upper level primary bedroom with sparkling new bath and walk in closet. This quiet North Stamford neighborhood location, with its level topography and multiple cul de sacs, makes walking and biking riding fun and also allows easy access to both New Canaan and Scotts Corners in Pound Ridge. It&apos;s a real beauty!",
